OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,FA coroner has raised concerns about a
OL,7,F"theme" of a "lack of observations" at
OL,8,Fa leading London hospital following
OL,9,Fthe death of a teenage girl.
OL,11,FBillie Wicks died age 16 after an
OL,12,Fasthma attack ` the first she had ever
OL,13,Fhad.
OL,15,FOn September 17 last year, her worried
OL,16,Fparents had rushed her to the Royal
OL,17,FFree Hospital in Hampstead, north
OL,18,FLondon.
