OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,FIt was a busy night in the A&E
OL,7,Fdepartment at the hospital, and a new
OL,8,Freport highlights how the department
OL,9,Fwas "understaffed" on the night Billie
OL,10,Fwas there.
OL,12,FSenior coroner for Inner North London,
OL,13,FMary Hassell, said that Billie should
OL,14,Fhave had routine checks, or
OL,15,Fobservations, taken every hour.
OL,17,FIf she had these observations, then
OL,18,Fmedics would have recognised the
OL,19,Fseverity of Billie's illness, Ms
OL,20,FHassell said.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
