OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,F"Billie was inappropriately discharged
OL,7,Fat approximately 3.30am without
OL,8,Fadequate repeat observations or senior
OL,9,Fclinical review, and so her asthma was
OL,10,Fnot diagnosed or treated.
OL,12,FIf it had been, she probably would
OL,13,Fhave survived," she wrote in a
OL,14,Fprevention of future deaths report.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
