OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,F"Billie should have had observations
OL,7,Fevery hour. If she had had these
OL,8,Fobservations, the emergency registrar
OL,9,Fwho discharged her would have
OL,10,Frecognised that she was not as well as
OL,11,Fhe thought, and would have sought
OL,12,Fsenior medical review.
OL,14,F"That senior medical review would have
OL,15,Fchanged the course of her management
OL,16,Fand saved her life."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Ms Hassell also mentioned
OL,19,Fthe case of Daniel Klosi ` who died
OL,20,Ffrom sepsis at the Royal Free in 2023.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@TO]
