OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,FDaniel was taken to hospital four
OL,7,Ftimes in the week running up to his
OL,8,Fdeath, and a report into the
OL,9,Fcircumstances surrounding his death
OL,10,Falso raises concern about observations.
OL,12,F"Following the inquest touching the
OL,13,Fdeath of Daniel Klosi, I wrote to you
OL,14,Fon August 16 2024 about a lack of
OL,15,Fobservations in the emergency
OL,16,Fdepartment of the Royal Free. Although
OL,17,Fthe circumstances were different,
OL,18,Fthere is a theme," Ms Hassell said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@RO]
