OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,F"I have heard this safety-netting
OL,7,Fadvice being described many, many
OL,8,Ftimes in different inquests. What
OL,9,Fworries me about it in this context is
OL,10,Fthat Billie's parents had brought her
OL,11,Fto hospital because they were
OL,12,Fconcerned. They were then reassured by
OL,13,Fhospital staff.
OL,15,F"It is therefore difficult to see how
OL,16,Fthis particular advice could be a
OL,17,Fmeaningful instruction.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
