OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,F"In reality, her parents' initial
OL,7,Fconcern was well placed and they had
OL,8,Fresponded to it appropriately by
OL,9,Fbringing Billie to hospital.
OL,11,F"When Billie began to deteriorate
OL,12,Fagain, her parents' natural instinct
OL,13,Fhad been blunted by their first visit
OL,14,Fto the hospital."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@QO]
