OL,3,CTeenager's life 'could have been
OL,4,Csaved' after asthma attack
OL,6,FShe also highlighted staffing issues
OL,7,Fin the department, adding: "At
OL,8,Finquest, I heard repeatedly that on
OL,9,Fthe night Billie attended, the Royal
OL,10,FFree emergency department was
OL,11,Funderstaffed, and that it remains
OL,12,Funderstaffed of doctors, nurses, and
OL,13,Feven a healthcare assistant who could
OL,14,Ftake basic observations."
OL,16,FThe report does say that a first case
OL,17,Fof asthma at the age of 16 without any
OL,18,Ffamily history is "unusual".
OL,26,@oD@\OUvD@YO]zD@SOUzD@[O]
