OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Royal Free
OL,7,FLondon said: "We would like to share
OL,8,Four heartfelt condolences with
OL,9,FBillie's family and to say how sorry
OL,10,Fwe are that she died while under our
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,F"Following an investigation into the
OL,14,Fcare provided to Billie, we have taken
OL,15,Fsteps to increase staffing levels in
OL,16,Fthe children's emergency department
OL,17,Fduring nights and weekends and improve
OL,18,Fthe process for alerting senior
OL,19,Fclinicians when an abnormal test
OL,20,Fresult is received.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOU
